We operate with the highest level of integrity and rigidly adhere to the policy of customer service, accountability and skill. We are a credible organization that stands behind its product. 
Extensive experience of several years and expertise of best artisans and craftsmen, we create designs that stand out. Be it your Kitchen, Bathroom, Vanity, Entertainment Unit, Bar or Walk-in Closet we have the skills to meet your every need. Our thorough knowledge of our trade is our biggest asset. From Planning to Designing to Manufacturing, we make sure you love every step along the way. We educate you about the industry, current trends and styles so that you make an informed decision.  We can turn your dream into reality without having to compromise on budget or quality.

profile:
Imperial Bathrooms is the bathroom mobility specialist. Having a little trouble getting into your tub? Our unique tub cutout conversions with the patented CleanCut™ bath steps can convert your existing bathtub into a safe and accessible step-in shower in hours. No need for a messy or expensive bathroom renovation. We can solve all your bathtub safety needs at a fraction of the cost and in less time! 

Imperial Bathrooms is a family owned and operated company. We've been serving senior care centers and home owners within the Greater Toronto Area since 2004. 


We offer bath safety solutions for people who may have a tough time getting into and out of their existing bathtub. Our unique bathtub cutout conversions are installed within just 2-3 hours and is the no-mess cost effective way to convert your existing bathtub into either a step-in shower or a walk-in. We offer the full line of CleanCut™ bath products which enables us to convert virtually any existing steel, cast iron, acrylic or fiberglass bathtub based on your needs and the type of bathtub you have. 


The 3 main products we carry are the CleanCut Step™ which converts your existing bathtub to a step-in shower. 


The CleanCut Ultra-Low™ which was specially designed to cut and convert higher wall acrylic or fiberglass bathtubs. 


And finally the CleanCut Convertible™ which has a 24" wide opening giving you the widest entry point into your bathtub and at any time if you or other family members what to have a full bath you would simple install the easy to use water-tight plug in seconds! 


In addition to the CleanCut™ bath products we also offer grab bar installation and adhesive anti-slip mats installation service. Just ask us about these additional bath safety products and we can easily install them at the same time as your bathtub cutout conversion using the CleanCut™ bath step.

services: We convert your existing bathtub into s step-in shower in just hours. Whether your bathtub is steel, cast iron or acrylic we can cut out a section of the tub and custom fit the resulting opening with one of the 3 CleanCut™ bath step options for easier tub access. In addition to our bathtub cutout service we also sell and install grab bars and bathtub anti-slip mats.

profile:
Since 1985, TUBS The Ultimate Bathroom Store has been a trendsetter in providing cutting edge, innovative kitchen and bathroom fixtures to homeowners and professionals. In fact, TUBS has helped launch a new era of inspiring concepts for the modern home, epitomizing functionality with unparalleled designs that have been featured in Style at Home Magazine, The Marilyn Denis Show and CityLine. From vanities and faucets to shower systems and tile, TUBS offers product from the top industry leading brands all under one roof.

As a privately owned Canadian company with international partners and an internal R&D team, we have the luxury of focusing on what we do best: creating innovative kitchen and bathroom fixtures at an affordable price point. Hence the motto we at TUBS live by: Affordable Luxury. 

Fueled with the tenacity to create industry leading, fashion-forward designs, we are expanding our collection of premium, contemporary kitchen and bathroom products for the ever-changing living space landscape. Visit TUBS today at one of our 5 showrooms conveniently located across the GTA.
